com.mood.jenaPlus

Class Participant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mood.jenaPlus.User
      • com.mood.jenaPlus.Participant

  • public class Participant
extends User
    This is the main participant class which contains a Jest Id for elastic search, a moodlist that contains their own list of moods, a following moodlist, and 2 lists for who they follow and who is following them.
    Author:
    Cecelia, Carlo
